      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "As of 2022, the jetty is more performant than the tomcat. There is no easier way to configure your custom thread pool implementation in tomcat but jetty. It&#39;s too easy to configure custom thread pool implementation in the jetty. That is important for creating a virtual thread per request. I think spring should replace tomcat with jetty in spring-boot-starter-web dependency."
